Flow Allocation Rate Enforcement policy for OpenIRATI.
Author: Kewin Rausch <kewin.rausch@create-net.org>

********************************************************************************
RESUME
********************************************************************************
This simply policy allows to extract, from the flow specifications, the average
bandwidth value and assign it to the rate dtcp configuration sending rate. Such
policy allows you to start AE instances which requires a personalized rate on 
the same QoS cube. 